 undergrad students to learn about grad school</p></div></div><div class='slide image-caption-container'><a href='http://nativestudies.ualberta.ca/programs/undergraduate-programs' class='image-shadow'><img class='fma-background' src="http://nativestudies.ualberta.ca/-/media/nativestudies/imagescontent/carousel-deadline-v3.jpg" /></a><div class="feature-caption caption"><h3><a href='http://nativestudies.ualberta.ca/programs/undergraduate-programs'>Fall 2016 Deadline Extension</a></h3><p>Find out more and apply online</p></div></div><div class='slide image-caption-container'><a href='http://nativestudies.ualberta.ca/about-us/deans-message' class='image-shadow'><img class='fma-background' src="http://nativestudies.ualberta.ca/-/media/nativestudies/navigation-images/carousel-andersen-interim-dean.jpg" /></a><div class="feature-caption caption"><h3><a href='http://nativestudies.ualberta.ca/about-us/deans-message'>Interim Dean Chris Andersen - Tân'si Ki'wow</a></h3><p>Welcome message from our Interim Dean</p></div></div>
